00001188                           283  * Subroutine    : UPDATE_DELTA_TIME
00001188                           284  * Description   : Calculates time passed since last frame
00001188                           285  *-----------------------------------------------------------
00001188                           286  UPDATE_DELTA_TIME:
00001188  48E7 E000                287      MOVEM.L D0-D2, -(SP)
0000118C  103C 0008                288      MOVE.B  #8, D0          ; Get elapsed milliseconds
00001190  4E4F                     289      TRAP    #15
00001192  23C1 0000162A            290      MOVE.L  D1, CURRENT_TIME
00001198                           291  
00001198  2439 0000162A            292      MOVE.L  CURRENT_TIME, D2
0000119E  94B9 00001626            293      SUB.L   LAST_TIME, D2  ; Subtract current time from last time to get elapsed milliseconds since
000011A4                           294      
000011A4                           295     * Prevent spikes when game paused etc
000011A4  B4BC 00000032            296      CMP.L  #50, D2      ; if more than or equal to 50 ms pass since last cycle
000011AA  6F00 0004                297      BLE     STORE_DELTA ; skip clamping
000011AE  7432                     298      MOVE.L  #50, D2     ; if current delta time > 50, clamp it to 50 (prevent spikes)
000011B0                           299  
000011B0                           300  STORE_DELTA:                
000011B0                           301  
000011B0  23C2 0000162E            302      MOVE.L  D2, DELTA_TIME
000011B6  23F9 0000162A 00001626   303      MOVE.L  CURRENT_TIME, LAST_TIME ; put current time into last for next cycle
