000015F6                           742  *-----------------------------------------------------------
000015F6                           743  * Subroutine    : Collision Check
000015F6                           744  * Description   : Axis-Aligned Bounding Box Collision Detection
000015F6                           745  * Algorithm checks for overlap on the 4 sides of the Player and 
000015F6                           746  * Enemy rectangles
000015F6                           747  * PLAYER_X <= ENEMY_X + ENEMY_W &&
000015F6                           748  * PLAYER_X + PLAYER_W >= ENEMY_X &&
000015F6                           749  * PLAYER_Y <= ENEMY_Y + ENEMY_H &&
000015F6                           750  * PLAYER_H + PLAYER_Y >= ENEMY_Y
000015F6                           751  *-----------------------------------------------------------
000015F6                           752  COLLISION:
000015F6  6100 FE68                753      BSR     PLAY_OPPS               ; Play Opps Wav
000015FA  23FC 00000000 000016C8   754      MOVE.L  #00, PLAYER_SCORE       ; Reset Player Score
00001604  4E75                     755      RTS                             ; Return to subroutine
00001606                           756  
00001606                           757  *-----------------------------------------------------------
00001606                           758  * Subroutine    : EXIT
00001606                           759  * Description   : Exit message and End Game
00001606                           760  *-----------------------------------------------------------
00001606                           761  EXIT:
